<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink" id="mwCZA"><a href="#cite_ref-14" id="mwCZE"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwCZI">↑ </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-14" class="mw-reference-text reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFMurrow2013" class="citation web cs1">Murrow, Pamela (February 4, 2013). <a href="https://allthingsliberty.com/2013/02/the-pine-tree-riot/" class="external text external" id="mwCZQ">"The Pine Tree Riot"</a>. <i id="mwCZU">Journal of the American Revolution</i><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCZY">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCZc">July 3,</span> 2024</span>.</cite></span></li>
